title: Emma Louise - Full Hearts And Empty Rooms (2011)
description: Hailing from Cairns and currently residing in Brisbane, emma louise is a singer-songwriter with an audacious yet sincere personality and infectious spirit. At just 19 years of age, her resume is impressive to say the least, winning 2 Q Song Awards in 2007 when she was 15 years old and having played alongside the likes of Sarah Blasko, Kate Miller-Heidke, Bob Evans, Tim Rogers and The Audreys.
